body.p:
This is a sample SBML model with spacial processes.
Original 3D microscopic image of SH-SY5Y cell was taken by Ryuichi Tanimoto
under the supervision of Noriko Hiroi.
The microscopic image was then passed to XitoSBML, an ImageJ plugin which creates an Spatial SBML model with segmented images.
All image processing including manipulating ImageJ and XitoSBML,
and mathematical modeling is performed by Kaito Ii under the supervision of
Kota Mashimo, Mitsunori Ozeki and Akira Funahashi.
